1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,280
I made a little world one afternoon

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:10,900
Just squares and skies of painted blue

3
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:14,160
A bird that never asked to fly

4
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:19,820
Until somebody pressed “Retry”

5
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:23,140
I thought a score would make it last

6
00:00:23,140 --> 00:00:28,800
A number no one could surpass

7
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,840
But numbers only learned to grow

8
00:00:32,830 --> 00:00:36,200
While all the names were left below

9
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:40,920
If every update hides a trace

10
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,480
Would someone still remember this place?

11
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:49,740
If every version fades away

12
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:54,420
Will anybody choose to stay?

13
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:57,640
Don’t chase the highest score tonight

14
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,880
Follow where the echoes hide

15
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:02,340
Some stories never reach “The End”

16
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:04,520
Until somebody plays again

17
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:06,680
If one more heart can hear this song

18
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:08,900
Then maybe nothing’s truly gone

19
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:11,220
The sky was never made to keep

20
00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:13,540
Only those who dared to leap

21
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:16,140
The world moved on to brighter screens

22
00:01:16,140 --> 00:01:18,480
To faster dreams and newer things

23
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,640
But somewhere underneath the code

24
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,880
The little road still waits alone

25
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:26,760
The final notes were always there

26
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:30,380
Just no one stayed to hear them end

27
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:32,620
You found the path

28
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:35,040
They couldn’t see

29
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:37,220
The missing line

30
00:01:37,220 --> 00:01:39,540
Inside of me

31
00:01:39,540 --> 00:01:40,700
No cheats

32
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:41,760
No myths

33
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,820
No perfect run

34
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:45,720
Just someone

35
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:50,040
Who finally listened

36
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:54,720
Thank you for reaching the end.
